E12WA.original: ~z~You know what they say about guys who spend time in South East Asia, man.
E12WA.translated: ~z~你也知道别人怎么评价去过东南亚的人吧，老兄。

E12WA.original: ~z~Yeah she's moved in with her folks.
~z~Get out there, man. There's hardbellies all over this city looking for a man with your gifts.
E12WA.translated: ~z~放宽心，兄弟。自由城能被你迷倒的小妞有的是。

E12WA.original: ~z~Man, I need this Club. Lost MC!
E12WA.translated: ~z~天，我离不开这个帮了。失落帮！

E12WA.original: ~z~Yeah? I thought we fucked up that country to all hell.
E12WA.translated: ~z~是吗？我还以为那个国家已经被我们糟蹋完了。

E12WA.original: ~z~You're my brother. I got your back.
~z~I got a gift, man. I'm blessed.
~z~The craziness, man. You're getting old. You can get out of this shit.
E12WA.translated: ~z~这种疯狂，兄弟。你年纪大了，可以远离这种生活了。

E12WA.original: ~z~People actually want to kill you out there.
E12WA.translated: ~z~因为军营外的人是真想杀你。

E12WA.original: ~z~If we do get sent down, I'm hoping it's together.
E12WA.translated: ~z~要是真坐牢了，希望我们还在一起。

E12WA.original: ~z~They can take everything, but you're still a fucking man, Terry. You got that.
E12WA.translated: ~z~他们能夺走一切，但你还是个男子汉，Terry。懂了吗。

E12WA.original: ~z~Herpes ain't a gift, man. It's a disease. You should keep that shit to yourself.
E12WA.translated: ~z~疱疹不是礼物，老兄。那是病毒。你还是自己独享吧。

E12WA.original: ~z~Same thing man, they all trying to fuck you.
~z~Johnny! I'm drowning here, man. I dunno.
~z~Shit, can we reach out to women as well? Don't think I could do without pussy for fifteen to twenty.
E12WA.translated: ~z~妈的，能不能再招点娘们？十几二十年不碰女人我可受不了。

E12WA.original: ~z~Yeah, well, you ain't got alimony to worry about. Nothing simple about that.
E12WA.translated: ~z~是吗，毕竟你不用愁抚养费。那可就不简单了。

E12WA.original: ~z~Don't laugh about it, man. I'm hurtin'.
~z~Like the country isn't run by five guys behind the scenes.
E12WA.translated: ~z~搞得跟这个国家不是幕后的五个人做的决策一样。

E12WA.original: ~z~Clay, man. You getting itchy feet? How long you been Stateside for?
E12WA.translated: ~z~Clay，兄弟，想去旅行吗？你回国多久了？

E12WA.original: ~z~Oh, they pay me, brother. They all pay for what I got.
E12WA.translated: ~z~她们付我钱，兄弟。她们为我的身家付钱。

E12WA.original: ~z~Not in the war, dumb ass. I was attached to the embassy.
E12WA.translated: ~z~不是说越战，傻逼。我被派到大使馆了。

E12WA.original: ~z~Alright, man. Then I will rephrase it. The fucking pricks running this country, man.
E12WA.translated: ~z~好吧，兄弟。那我换一个说法。管理国家的都是傻逼，兄弟。

E12WA.original: ~z~Fuck, man. I thought the outlaw life would save me from that shit.
E12WA.translated: ~z~操，兄弟。我还以为法外狂徒就不会有这种闹心事了。

E12WA.original: ~z~Very funny... sometimes, I find myself thinking what the fuck happened to my country?
E12WA.translated: ~z~好好笑哦...有时候我在想，我的祖国怎么成了这个样子？

E12WA.original: ~z~Sometimes, I think prison would be better.
~z~I hope not. Hope he heads out west or something.
E12WA.translated: ~z~但愿不会吧。希望他会去西部之类的地方。

E12WA.original: ~z~You thought you'd be an army man?
~z~Billy was cool back then, weren't he?
~z~You retiring me? Gonna take me 'round the back and shoot me like a lame horse?
E12WA.translated: ~z~你叫我退休？绕到我身后，像对待瘸腿马一样给我一枪？

E12WA.original: ~z~Just like the old days, huh brother?
~z~I dunno, seems like a lot of people in Liberty City wanna kill me, man.
E12WA.translated: ~z~不好说，我在自由城似乎也被不少人给盯上了。

E12WA.original: ~z~You back with us, dude? What were we saying? Oh yeah...
E12WA.translated: ~z~还回来吗，老兄？我们在说啥呢？哦对...

E12WA.original: ~z~Shit, no wonder I spend most my time carrying your ass.
E12WA.translated: ~z~妈的，怪不得我经常跟你这逼崽子在一块。

E12WA.original: ~z~Alright, then. In that case, I guess things couldn't get any worse than they are right now.
E12WA.translated: ~z~那好吧。这么一说，现在应该是糟糕透顶了。

E12WA.original: ~z~Then they threaten to repossess my bike...
E12WA.translated: ~z~现在他们还威胁要收回我的摩托...

E12WA.original: ~z~That's life in twenty first century America, my brother. We woke up in a nightmare.
E12WA.translated: ~z~这就是二十一世纪美国的生活，好兄弟。醒来仍是噩梦。

E12WA.original: ~z~I'd like to see 'em try and repossess my balls, man. That'll be the day.
E12WA.translated: ~z~我倒想看看他们能不能收回我的蛋，兄弟。差不多得了。

E12WA.original: ~z~Man, I liked her. Going off with that fucking Deadbeat. Shit!
E12WA.translated: ~z~天，我喜欢她。结果跟那个死妈天使跑了。操！

E12WA.original: ~z~Dude, you're in The Lost. You're just looking out for your brothers.
E12WA.translated: ~z~老兄，你是失落帮的一员。你只是在照应兄弟罢了。

E12WA.original: ~z~Crazy Colin's now a man of God.
~z~I guess it's a good thing shit's so fucked up then.
~z~Yes, Jesus. Batshit fucking crazy he is, whole family has gone into hiding.
E12WA.translated: ~z~是啊，上帝啊。他是彻头彻尾地疯了，我全家都躲起来了。

E12WA.original: ~z~You old, Clay. But you ain't that old.
~z~That shit catches up with you, man.
~z~Might do her some good getting shit from her parents after all the crap she gave you.
E12WA.translated: ~z~给你找了那么多麻烦，也该轮到她的父母给她找点麻烦了。

E12WA.original: ~z~Always thought I'd be an army man.
~z~Well, I swore to my daddy I'd never be a cop.
E12WA.translated: ~z~这个嘛，我对我爸发过誓，绝不当条子。

E12WA.original: ~z~I don't need your pity man. And she ain't worth your pity, not no more.
E12WA.translated: ~z~我不需要你同情，兄弟。她也不配被同情，现在的她不配。

E12WA.original: ~z~I can see how that pisses you off, man. Fuck it all, I guess.
E12WA.translated: ~z~我能理解你为什么生气，兄弟。操他妈的。

E12WA.original: ~z~I mean, you got a wife and kid. You got responsibilities.
E12WA.translated: ~z~我是说你有老婆孩子。你有家庭的责任。

E12WA.original: ~z~I'm on a fucking treadmill, man. Feel I'm running and if I stop everything goes to shit.
E12WA.translated: ~z~我就像是在跑步机上，兄弟。不能停下来，否则一切就都完了

E12WA.original: ~z~Clay, man, you get the respect. Got to admire a man who served his country and saw some action overseas.
E12WA.translated: ~z~Clay，老兄，注意着点。必须对为国效力征战海外的战士心怀敬意。

E12WA.original: ~z~But, man, it's the whole culture. The vibe.
E12WA.translated: ~z~但兄弟，我更爱那种文化，那种氛围。

E12WA.original: ~z~You okay Jim? Anyway, as we were saying.
E12WA.translated: ~z~你还好吗，Jim？总之，之前也说过了。

E12WA.original: ~z~No, man. It's all still there. Still going strong.
E12WA.translated: ~z~不，老兄。它还好好的，依然在发展。

E12WA.original: ~z~Know what the American dream is? The house, the car, the family - that bullshit.
E12WA.translated: ~z~知道美国梦是啥吗？大房子，小轿车，一家人。纯放屁。

E12WA.original: ~z~It was mine, man. I fucking paid those mortgage payments.
E12WA.translated: ~z~我的房子，老兄。房贷是我还的。

E12WA.original: ~z~You don't mean that. She loves you.
~z~I don't think so, man. Wouldn't be fair.
E12WA.translated: ~z~我可不同意，老兄。这样不公平。

E12WA.original: ~z~He could smoke more 'n anyone. Drink more n' anyone. Ride harder...
E12WA.translated: ~z~他抽烟比谁都猛，喝酒比谁都多，骑车也是...

E12WA.original: ~z~I know, brother. But life is hard, man. Take happiness where you can find it.
E12WA.translated: ~z~我懂的，兄弟。但是人生苦短，老兄。还是要及时行乐啊。

E12WA.original: ~z~You think those supremacist motherfuckers wouldn't go for my Jewish ass day and night?
E12WA.translated: ~z~你以为那些种族主义者就待见我这个犹太人了？

E12WA.original: ~z~You're getting too slow as well as too old, buddy. Anyway.
E12WA.translated: ~z~你年纪也大了，速度也慢了，伙计。真的。

E12WA.original: ~z~I love you brothers. The heartache... the pain, man. It's good to have you boys. You're constant.
E12WA.translated: ~z~我爱你们，兄弟们。爱到心痛...爱到痛苦，兄弟。有你们在真好，一直都在。

E12WA.original: ~z~I don't fucking know... seriously fucking weird coffee by the look of things.
E12WA.translated: ~z~我他妈也不知道...看样子应该是什么狗屎咖啡吧。

E12WA.original: ~z~You must have a whole lot of spare food stamps then. Good for you.
E12WA.translated: ~z~那你手头一定有很多食品券吧。挺好的。

E12WA.original: ~z~It wasn't just that. I mean I love the women out there.
E12WA.translated: ~z~何止是那样。我的确喜欢那边的娘们。

E12WA.original: ~z~Colin the ex man of God, new man of heroin relapse.
E12WA.translated: ~z~曾信上帝的Colin，现在又在吸海洛因了。

E12WA.original: ~z~Don't say nothing about this country, Terry. I fought for this country. My friends died for this country.
E12WA.translated: ~z~别对这个国家逼逼赖赖，Terry。我为这个国家而战，我的朋友为了这个国家牺牲。

E12WA.original: ~z~We can start an all inclusive prison gang. Crossing lines. Reachin' out to every creed and color?
E12WA.translated: ~z~可以在牢里建一个包容的帮派。打破隔阂，对所有肤色和信仰开放。

E12WA.original: ~z~In her own way, sure. Only problem is, she's a psycho.
E12WA.translated: ~z~在她看来，是的。但问题是，她是个疯子。

E12WA.original: ~z~I don't know. But not good, I imagine.
~z~I strictly pay with cash, Terry. Keeps things simple.
~z~Man, I knew God moved in mysterious ways, but that is fucking perverse.
E12WA.translated: ~z~天，我知道主的意图难以捉摸，但这也太扯了吧。

E12WA.original: ~z~Clay, dude, where was the best place the army stationed you?
E12WA.translated: ~z~Clay，老兄，你对军队的哪个驻派地最满意？

E12WA.original: ~z~Johnny Klebitz! Leading the way. You're a real figure of authority, man.
E12WA.translated: ~z~Johnny Klebitz！带头冲锋。你的官帽可真高啊，老兄。

E12WA.original: ~z~Don't worry, man. It's a zen-like place.
~z~I know... I know... Shit, growing up in the neighborhood.
E12WA.translated: ~z~我懂...我懂...妈的，想想我小时候的环境，

E12WA.original: ~z~He was, man. He sure as shit was.
~z~I served this place and now look at it, man. Place is a dump.
E12WA.translated: ~z~我为国家效过力，再看看现在。国家成了粪坑。

E12WA.original: ~z~Same old shit. Dodging bullets when I'm out and whatever Jackie can throw at me when I'm home. You?
E12WA.translated: ~z~老样子。出门在外躲子弹，回家躲老婆的暴风雨。你呢？

E12WA.original: ~z~Unfortunately not. My daddy's scared he's going to come back to the farm.
E12WA.translated: ~z~天不如人意啊。我爸很担心他会回家里的农场。

E12WA.original: ~z~I'm responsible for my brothers too, Johnny. You included. This shit don't end good.
E12WA.translated: ~z~我还要对兄弟负责，Johnny。对你也是。不会轻易结束的。

E12WA.original: ~z~Poor thing. I'm sorry for you two.
~z~The rich get richer and the poor die.
~z~It's control man. They make you want that shit so they can trap you.
E12WA.translated: ~z~都是为了控制你。给你画一个饼，你就掉进陷阱了。

E12WA.original: ~z~Same old bills biting me in the ass, man.
~z~Johnny, you know what gets me, man?
~z~I know, man, I know. You ain't turning snitch on us are you?
E12WA.translated: ~z~我知道，兄弟，我知道。你该不会出卖我们了吧？

E12WA.original: ~z~I dunno how you do it, Jim. One woman and she drives you fucking crazy?
E12WA.translated: ~z~我有点想不明白，Jim。光一个女人就能把你逼疯吗？

E12WA.original: ~z~Oh, I'm good. Real good. Found me somethin' fresh. Nice little mattress thrasher.
E12WA.translated: ~z~噢，我很好。非常好。刚找了个新玩具。超级棒的小骚逼。

E12WA.original: ~z~Rock and roll don't ever end so well, brother.
E12WA.translated: ~z~摇滚从来就没有善始善终，兄弟。

E12WA.original: ~z~Yeah, it's a handicapping system. They put the strongest of us with the weakest. Evens us out.
E12WA.translated: ~z~这就是差点系统。把最强跟最弱分到一组，拉成平均。

E12WA.original: ~z~Lost the train of thought there, didn't we, Clay?
~z~The shit that happened to the kids in my class... I swore to my momma I'd never touch that stuff.
E12WA.translated: ~z~我同班同学的那些遭遇...我对我妈发过誓，绝不会碰这一行。

E12WA.original: ~z~You know what the best thing about travelling the world is, Johnny?
E12WA.translated: ~z~你知道周游世界最棒的是哪一点吗，Johnny？

E12WA.original: ~z~Pretty shit, man. Only way they could get worse is if you or Clay turned snitch.
E12WA.translated: ~z~糟透了，伙计。想要更糟的话就只有你或Clay叛变告发了。

E12WA.original: ~z~Feds don't need snitches, man. They can pluck conversations outta thin air.
E12WA.translated: ~z~政府不需要有人告发。现在这样说话他们也能听到。

E12WA.original: ~z~But the women are a part of the culture?
E12WA.translated: ~z~可娘们也是文化的一部分吧？
~z~吃得饱汉堡...铛铛钟炸鸡...各种傻逼...

E12WA.original: ~z~Then you're working like a dog - breaking your back - and soon there's nothing left.
E12WA.translated: ~z~让你像条狗一样卖力，榨干你的精力，然后变成一具空壳。

E12WA.original: ~z~That I'm a drug dealing, murdering gang member.
E12WA.translated: ~z~我是一个杀人贩毒的帮派份子。

E12WA.original: ~z~It's a fucking dream and nothing more.
~z~Just keep 'em away from my fucking menorah, man. That's all I ask.
E12WA.translated: ~z~你别往我的大烛台边上放就行，兄弟。就这点要求。

E12WA.original: ~z~I'm hopin' forever. Don't think I'd like doing a bid.
~z~Not so much when I realized war was just about getting the fat cats fatter though.
E12WA.translated: ~z~直到我发现，战争其实是权贵的敛财工具。

E12WA.original: ~z~Yuppies taking bonuses while workers lose their pensions?
E12WA.translated: ~z~雅皮士拿着分红，工人却失去了养老金？

E12WA.original: ~z~Think we can resume our conversation. That alright with you, Clay?
E12WA.translated: ~z~那还是接着聊吧。你没问题吧，Clay？

E12WA.original: ~z~So Colin, my brother - rang me the other day.
~z~Place was always a dump brother, difference now is the people ain't buying the bullshit no more.
E12WA.translated: ~z~这里一直都是粪坑，兄弟。只不过现代人对那些屁话不买账了而已。

E12WA.original: ~z~You must have an exotic array of sexually transmitted diseases by now.
E12WA.translated: ~z~你身上肯定有来自异国他乡的各种性病了吧。
~z~是吗？发生什么了？没出人命吧？

E12WA.original: ~z~You still ride like a bitch, man.
~z~It's my duty to share this with all the females I can.
E12WA.translated: ~z~把这份礼物分享给所有女人是我的使命。

E12WA.original: ~z~How come I'm always stuck with you? Seems like wherever I go, you're right there next to me.
E12WA.translated: ~z~我怎么一直跟你在一块儿？好像无论去哪儿，你都在我旁边。

E12WA.original: ~z~You'll meet someone, Clay. It'll all make sense.
E12WA.translated: ~z~等你结婚就明白了，Clay。再正常不过了。

E12WA.original: ~z~Fucking Horse got sentimental right before he turned snitch.
E12WA.translated: ~z~傻逼Horse出卖我们之前也是这么感性。

E12WA.original: ~z~Hey, it don't count if you're paying for it.
~z~For real, man. Fool found God inside and now he's trying to convert anyone in a ten mile radius.
E12WA.translated: ~z~真的，老兄。那傻逼心里有上帝了，见着个人就跟他传教。

E12WA.original: ~z~I'm feeling the calm of a man whose life can't get any worse.
E12WA.translated: ~z~我已经能感受到那种反正不可能更糟的平静了。

E12WA.original: ~z~Dunno, but I suspect you're gonna tell me it's the women.
E12WA.translated: ~z~不知道，不过我猜你想说娘们。

E12WA.original: ~z~First the mayor takes away our constitutional right to bear arms...
E12WA.translated: ~z~先是被市长夺走了持械的宪法权利...

E12WA.original: ~z~The honey-colored girl. I love America's Next Top Hooker.
E12WA.translated: ~z~蜂蜜色的姑娘。我爱死《美国新花魁》了

E12WA.original: ~z~They got all the American shit you need on base:
E12WA.translated: ~z~基地里还是美国本土那股味儿：

E12WA.original: ~z~The Federal Government monitoring our every move?
E12WA.translated: ~z~监视着我们一举一动的联邦政府？

E12WA.original: ~z~Dude, being in the army, I don't get how you could stay away from America that long.
E12WA.translated: ~z~老兄，一直在外服役，我都不知道你怎么能在海外待这么久。

E12WA.original: ~z~Don't put that round, man. I'm clean. I wrap my presents before I put 'em under the tree.
E12WA.translated: ~z~别提这茬，兄弟。我很干净。我会套上套子再把礼物放到圣诞树下的。

E12WA.original: ~z~Sure do. Squirrely little bag o' bones that you were.
E12WA.translated: ~z~当然了。那会儿你疯疯癫癫皮包骨头。

E12WA.original: ~z~I still can't get over it, man.
~z~I mean, the boys in there wouldn't take too kindly to my associations with men of your pale pigmentation.
E12WA.translated: ~z~主要是里面的人未必见得我跟你这种白皮交朋友。

E12WA.original: ~z~Man, land of the free became the land of the fucking macchi-fucking-ato.
E12WA.translated: ~z~天，自由之都成了他妈玛奇朵之都。

E12WA.original: ~z~Let's enjoy this, boys - freedom. We ain't dead and we ain't in jail. How long can it last?
E12WA.translated: ~z~尽情享受吧，各位——享受自由。我们一没有死，二没坐牢。这日子能持续多久？

E12WA.original: ~z~They can tap any phone they wanna. Shit, federal witnesses became obsolete at the turn of the century.
E12WA.translated: ~z~所有人的手机都被监听了。妈的，证人保护计划在世纪之交的时候过时了。

E12WA.original: ~z~That's funny, cause the army still got a bee in their bonnet about homosexuality.
E12WA.translated: ~z~有意思了，因为军队对同性恋的态度还是那么纠结。

E12WA.original: ~z~Get this guy away from me. Will one of you have a serious fucking conversation?
E12WA.translated: ~z~有多远滚多远。就不能来个正经说话的主吗？

E12WA.original: ~z~You lost that right when you got your first felony, man.
E12WA.translated: ~z~初犯重罪以后你就不能持械了，兄弟。

E12WA.original: ~z~Plus, it ain't like here where the news scares you into thinking people want to kill you.
E12WA.translated: ~z~不过，军营里可没有给你灌输被害妄想的新闻。

E12WA.original: ~z~I wouldn't ever do that to you.
~z~Shit, is it them payments to your ex wife? The brothers can help.
E12WA.translated: ~z~妈的，是不是前妻的抚养费？兄弟们能帮你。

E12WA.original: ~z~Johnny, man, rip up your fucking credit cards.
~z~Only action I care to speak about's the between the sheets kind.
E12WA.translated: ~z~我想聊的征战只有在床上的南征北战。

E12WA.original: ~z~How long's this go on for, Jim?
~z~Much as I like that show, I was talking about politicians not hookers.
E12WA.translated: ~z~虽然我也喜欢，但我问的是政治投票，不是选秀。

E12WA.original: ~z~Shit, maybe three years. Ever since I was reborn into civilian life.
E12WA.translated: ~z~妈的，差不多有三年吧。一退伍我就想去旅行了。

E12WA.original: ~z~In a way. Only problem is now I know how the story's going to end.
E12WA.translated: ~z~也许吧。只是现在我知道故事的结局了。

E12WA.original: ~z~What gets me is these fucking assholes talking politics like it matters.
E12WA.translated: ~z~我最气不过那帮煞有介事地聊政治的混蛋。

E12WA.original: ~z~Jim? You remember when I joined up?
